The Portland Hearts of Pine announced the signings of two more defenders for the 2026 season.

New to the club will be Esteban Espinosa, 23, who most recently was with RWDM Molenbeek in Belgium and previously spent two seasons with Botafogo B in Brazil before being loaned to Louletano B in Portugal.

